ren Nunis)</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/people-walking-inside-amazon-building-surrounded-with-plants-O-Unw-ho1kQ?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄的照片</figcaption></figure></div><p>但该机场并不是某种为了给路过的人留下深刻印象而建造的波将金计划。这座城市本身充满了建筑，虽然不如机场那么漂亮，但绝对奢华且令人印象深刻。这篇文章顶部的照片——一个名为滨海一号的巨大办公/零售/住宅综合体——只是众多此类奇迹之一。</p><p>新加坡的建设令人难以置信——几乎和东京一样发达。与东京一样，随处可见的大型建筑具有精致的未来主义外观和一尘不染的修剪整齐的场地，给人一种身处一艘巨大的有人居住的宇宙飞船内的感觉。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg" width="678" height="900" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:900,&quot;width&quot;:678,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:171675,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F171d7277-493c-4264-bfa4-44e7cd516a17_678x900.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但新加坡的建筑环境更令人印象深刻的是<em>绿化</em>。新加坡位于海边，距离赤道仅几英里，因此几乎一直炎热潮湿。在这种环境下，避免城市被雨林淹没的最便宜的方法就是清除所有植物。相反，新加坡决定成为<a href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/environment/article/green-urban-landscape-cities-Singapore">世界上最环保的城市</a>。这需要大量的资金和努力才能实现，同时又不让这座城市看起来像丛林中的废墟（就像<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/taipei-urbanism">台北的部分地区</a>一样）。所有这些树叶都必须进行景观美化，而这并不便宜。所以新加坡美丽的绿化确实是财富的壮观体现。</p><p>事实上，绿色植物不仅存在于建筑物<em>周围</em>，也存在于建筑物周围。它也在他们<em>身上</em>。新加坡在“<a href="https://www.vagabondjourney.com/plants-on-buildings-skyrise-greenery-in-singapore/">空中绿化</a>”方面处于世界领先地位，即用树叶覆盖塔楼的外部。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061-8a55-0fc50f69c989_1024x771.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1aed804f-6d86-4061