een&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;100%&quot;,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2526fe3a-ad43-412f-9df1-5997312a9c1f_1292x680.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2526fe3a-ad43-412f-9df1-5997312a9c1f_1292x680.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2526fe3a-ad43-412f-9df1-5997312a9c1f_1292x680.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2526fe3a-ad43-412f-9df1-5997312a9c1f_1292x680.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">地图由<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=139254470">Specialgst</a>提供</figcaption></figure></div><p>以色列-加沙战争引发了许多激烈的言论。最大的话题之一是，美国对以色列的支持将导致其<a href="https://twitter.com/ForeignPolicy/status/1715563624704483356">失去“全球南方”国家的支持</a>。我不知道这是否属实——穆斯林国家似乎至少对美国感到恼火，但<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2023/10/25/pro-israel-rallies-allowed-in-india-but-palestine-solidarity-sees-crackdown">印度似乎</a>更支持以色列。但无论如何，这引起了我对“全球北方”和“全球南方”类别使用方式的高度质疑——不仅在网上讨论中，而且在联合国等官方组织中也是如此。</p><p>许多人将“全球南方”与“发展中国家”互换使用，因为地球北部国家通常比南部国家更富裕。事实上，早在 2021 年，我就在一篇有关全球发展的帖子中使用了它： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;e03a655e-2f43-4147-b77e-4f5b0f2cd1aa&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;The other day on Twitter we were discussing the &#8220;Global South&#8221; (because Brad DeLong had a podcast about it). So I thought I&#8217;d do a post checking in on the general status of developing countries, because there have been some interesting developments in recent years that might change our overall &#8230;&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Checking in on the Global South&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2021-03-15T08:26:59.495Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd670ce83-4b78-4ac8-8db3-e8fab54fef54_1024x683.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/checking-in-on-the-global-south&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:33710182,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:28,&quot;comment_count&quot;:27,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}"></div><p>但一旦你试图将世界上所有国家实际上分为两组，你就会遇到困难。例如，1980 年，一个独立的国际委员会发布的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brandt_Report">《勃兰特报告》</a> ，划出了一条清晰的界限： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png" width="700" height="407" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d2646870-8e89-478b-b495-a0a2c5777f3b_700x407.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:407,&quot;width&quot;:700,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:152929,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:f